91_ukJ7I.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/bd/6b/263191_ukJ7I.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/bd/6b/263191_ukJ7I.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/bd/6b/263191_ukJ7I.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/bd/6b/263191_ukJ7I.jpg"},"summary":"　　又是平静的一天，汤姆和杰瑞之间爆发了新的大战，虽然汤姆占有体形优势，却终究斗不过杰瑞的机敏，因此饱受戏耍。在躲避汤姆追杀的过程中，杰瑞偶然躲进了一瓶隐形墨水之中，出来后竟发现自己的下半身完全消失了。短暂的惊诧过后，他很快发现隐形的原委，于是杰瑞将全身都涂上了隐形墨水。 \r\n　　另一方面，汤姆还逡巡在杰瑞的洞口前，布下种种陷阱等待小老鼠上钩，却不知道隐形的杰瑞已经悄悄来到他的身后。在此之后，倒霉的汤姆不得不与这个形同空气般的老对手展开连番对决。前所未有的战争旋即展开，而各种有趣的笑料也纷至沓来……","name":"The Invisible Mouse","name_cn":"隐形墨水","tags":[{"name":"短片","count":20,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1947","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"欧美","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"猫和老鼠","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"美国","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1940s","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"米高梅","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"剧场版","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"8(+3)","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1940-1949","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Short","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"原创","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Short_film","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"隐形墨水"},{"key":"上映年度","value":"1947-09-27"},{"key":"片长","value":"7分钟"},{"key":"话数","value":"1"}],"rating":{"rank":0,"total":39,"count":{"1":1,"2":0,"3":0,"4":0,"5":1,"6":3,"7":20,"8":12,"9":1,"10":1},"score":7.2},"total_episodes":0,"collection":{"on_hold":1,"dropped":4,"wish":6,"collect":86,"doing":3},"id":263191,"eps":1,"meta_tags":["剧场版"],"volumes":0,"series":false,"locked":false,"nsfw":false,"type":2}]